<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT28">
<l>ituvilaṅkai yīṭaḻiyak kaṭṭiya cētu</l>
<l>vituvilaṅku vāliyai vīḻttatu vituvilaṅkai</l>
<l>tāṉoṭuṅka vilnuṭaṅkat taṇtā rirāvaṇaṉai</l>
<l>yūṉoṭuṅka veytā ṉukappu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This, the bridge that was built so that the might of Laṅkā would be ruined;</l>
<l>This, the felling of the animal Vālin,</l>
<l>These are the joys of [Rāma] who dispatched [arrows]</l>
<l rend="indent">In such a way that [His] bow became bent,</l>
<l rend="indent">So that Laṅkā became subservient,</l>
<l rend="indent">So that the body of Rāvaṇa with cool garlands slid [down].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
